en-US.description:
VocaBoost helps you improve your GRE vocabulary in an effective way.
This app is designed to assist non-native English users in learning English and preparing for the GRE exam. It has about 1500 most common GRE vocabulary and phrases. You can review vocabulary in English, Chinese, and Spanish.
en-US.promoText: Review 1500 most common GRE vocabulary and prepare for the exam effortlessly. We support English, Chinese, and Spanish.
en-US.title: VocabBoost
en-US.subtitle: GRE vocabulary learning tool
